"View the most popular backgrounds from our community for each category and click on the category name to view everything in that category."="查看来自我们社区的各品类最热门背景，点击类型名称可查看该类型中的内容。"
"View the most popular backgrounds from our community."="查看来自我们社区的最热门背景。"
