"Would you like Deskscapes to attempt to fix this?"="是否希望 DeskScapes 尝试修复此问题?"
"Would you like Deskscapes to attempt to switch to the Windows Aero theme so you can use Deskscapes?"="是否希望 DeskScapes 尝试切换至 Windows Aero 主题，从而使用 DeskScapes?"
"Would you like DeskScapes to change this setting?"="是否希望 DeskScapes 更改此设置?"
"You appear to be running on battery power and you have told DeskScapes not to run when on battery power.  Would you like to enable DeskScapes when on battery power?"="你的计算机似乎正以电池供电，且你已告知 DeskScapes 不要在使用电池供电期间运行。  希望在使用电池供电时启用 DeskScapes 吗?"
"You can add a category to the favourites list from the categories page."="可以从类别页面将类别添加至收藏列表。"
"You can add an author to the favourites list from the authors page."="可以从作者页面将作者添加至收藏列表。"
"You can add backgrounds to a playlist from the apply button on any background."="可从任意背景的应用按钮将背景添加到播放列表。"
"You can add backgrounds to this playlist and apply this to your desktop."="可将背景添加至该播放列表，并将该播放列表应用至桌面。"
"You can also alter how this background appears."="您还可以更改此背景的显示方式。"
"You can change the timeout or disable screensavers from the operating system screensavers control panel."="可从操作系统的屏幕保护程序控制面板更改屏幕保护程序的延时或将其禁用。"
"You can customise your background by applying effects to it when you have clicked on the image by selecting other pages on the open page."="当您点击图像时，您可以通过在打开页面上选择其他页面来自定义您的背景。"
"You can even create advanced animations using the powerful creator tool."="使用强大的创作工具，甚至可以打造出高级的动画。"
"-You can record video from games or other applications by pressing WIN + G to access the XBox Game Bar.  WIN + ALT + R will start and stop a recording automatically of the currently focused application or game."="- 可通过按下 WIN + G 访问 XBox Game Bar 的方式，从游戏或其他应用程序中进行视频的录制。  按下 WIN + ALT + R 可自动基于焦点当前所在的应用程序或游戏进行录制或停止录制。"
"You generated a new wallpaper but haven't saved it. "="您生成了一张新壁纸但尚未保存。 "
"You have selected multiple backgrounds and are in random mode.  You can disable this by selecting a single background."="您已选择多个背景并处于随机模式。您可以通过选择单个背景来禁用此模式。"
"You have selected multiple backgrounds and are in random mode.  You can disable this by selecting a single background.\n\nAdjust settings using the button below."="您已选择多个背景并处于随机模式。您可以通过选择单个背景来禁用此模式。\n\n使用下方按钮调整设置。"
"You have selected the random backgrounds folder so are in random mode.  You can disable this by selecting a different folder and can add to this by right clicking on backgrounds and picking the add to random option."="您已选择随机背景文件夹，因此处于随机模式。您可以通过选择其他文件夹来禁用此模式，也可以通过右键点击背景并选择“添加到随机”选项来添加。"
"You must give this combined effect a name"="必须为这套组合效果起名"
"Your screensaver has been applied"="已应用屏幕保护程序"
"Your trial period has expired\nPlease purchase DeskScapes 8 to continue using it."="您的试用期已结束\n请购买 DeskScapes 8 以继续使用。"

