"Estimated wall-clock for this restyle:"="本次风格重塑的预计实际耗时："
"   - CPU mode: 5 to 10 minutes"="   - CPU 模式：5 至 10 分钟"
"   - This iGPU: 20 to 35 minutes"="   - 此核显：20 至 35 分钟"
"You can switch back to the iGPU later from the GPU picker in AI Settings."="您稍后可以在 AI 设置的 GPU 选择器中切换回核显。"
"Integrated GPUs are significantly underpowered compared to discrete cards for AI workloads. Typical wall-clock times for a FLUX.2 restyle:"="对于 AI 工作负载，集成 GPU 的性能远逊于独立显卡。FLUX.2 风格重塑的典型实际耗时："
"   - Modern AMD Ryzen 8000G / 7040 (RDNA3 Radeon 780M): 3 to 6 minutes"="   - 现代 AMD Ryzen 8000G / 7040（RDNA3 Radeon 780M）：3 至 6 分钟"
"   - Intel Core Ultra (Arc-class integrated): 4 to 8 minutes"="   - Intel Core Ultra（Arc 级集成显卡）：4 至 8 分钟"
"   - AMD Ryzen 5000G / 4000G (Vega): 8 to 15 minutes"="   - AMD Ryzen 5000G / 4000G（Vega）：8 至 15 分钟"
"   - Intel Iris Xe (11th-13th gen): 10 to 20 minutes"="   - Intel Iris Xe（第 11-13 代）：10 至 20 分钟"
"   - Older APUs / pre-Iris-Xe Intel: 20 minutes or more"="   - 较旧的 APU / Iris Xe 之前的 Intel：20 分钟或更长"
"You can cancel anytime from the preview screen. For routine use a discrete GPU with 6 GB or more VRAM is strongly recommended."="您可以随时从预览屏幕取消。对于日常使用，强烈建议使用具有 6 GB 或更多显存的独立 GPU。"
"Use CPU mode (recommended)"="使用 CPU 模式（推荐）"
"Much faster on this hardware. Routes the entire pipeline to your CPU."="在此硬件上快得多。将整个流程路由到您的 CPU。"
"Use this iGPU anyway"="仍使用此核显"
"Run on the 2-CU display iGPU. Expect 20+ minutes per image."="在 2-CU 显示核显上运行。预计每张图像需 20 分钟以上。"
"Proceed anyway"="仍要继续"
"Start the restyle. You can cancel from the preview screen at any time."="开始风格重塑。您可以随时从预览屏幕取消。"
"Don't show this warning again"="不再显示此警告"
